<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们去火车站接妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为他们非常喜欢火车站，所以提前一个小时到了那里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>坐在候车室里等妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车到达时，彼得、菲利斯和鲍比跑出去看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们以为只有一两个人，但是站台里却站满了人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们只能看到人们的后背。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家在议论着什么，一定是有什么事情发生了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他很奇怪。”一个男人说，“我们应该报警。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，应该打电话给医院！”一个女人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62408</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>站长大声说：“大家请让一让！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是人群并没有让开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，孩子们听到一个特别的声音，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个男人在说外语——一种孩子们从没听过的语言。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他在说什么？”有人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听上去像法语。”站长说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是法语。”彼得说，“我知道法语怎么发音。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人群散开，大家想看看是谁在说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，彼得可以看到那个男人了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他穿着奇怪的衣服、留着长长的头发、眼神狂放。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你会法语，你来跟他聊聊。”一个女人对彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，男人跑上前来，抓住彼得的手，开始对他说法语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他说什么？”站长问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听不懂。”彼得回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>站长把男人带进候车室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我妈妈会说法语。”鲍比对站长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈会坐下一班火车回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们和男人一起等待的时候，彼得想到了一个办法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从口袋里拿出一个信封，里面是各个国家的邮票。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得给男人看意大利的邮票，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>指了指邮票，又指了指他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是男人摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着给他看了一张挪威和西班牙的邮票。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人又摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，男人拿走信封，自己在邮票里找。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是俄国人！”菲利斯看到他拿起一张俄国的邮票。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈的火车到站了，站长把她带进候车室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>俄国人站起来鞠了个躬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194975</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈和男人用法语交流。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一开始句子比较短，后来句子越来越长。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们看着妈妈的表情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们可以猜到男人在告诉妈妈一件让她又生气又伤心的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后妈妈说：“没什么事，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的车票丢了，而且还生病了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果您不介意的话，我现在带他回家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“夫人，您应该谨慎点儿！”站长说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不用担心。”妈妈愉快地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他在俄国很有名，他写过许多非常棒的书。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们回到家，妈妈让那个俄国人睡在她的房间里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为只有妈妈的房间才有壁炉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>之后，鲍比带着医生来到房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在房间里，她看到妈妈黑色的大箱子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>平时箱子是锁着的，但是现在是开着的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>箱子里有爸爸的衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为什么爸爸没有带走衣服？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比的心砰砰直跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>